ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce et d'industrie Beauharnois-Valleyfield (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE ET D'INDUSTRIE BEAUHARNOIS-VALLEYFIELD, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from Salabery-de-Valleyfield, Beauharnois, St-Étienne de Beauharnois, St-Stanislas de Kostka and St-Louis-de-Gonzague to the municipalities of Salabery-de-Valleyfield, St-Louis-de-Gonzague, St-Stanislas-de-Kostka, Beauharnois, St-Étienne de Beauharnois, Saint-Anicet, Huntingdon, Hinchinbrooke, Godmanchester, Elgin, Dundee, Havelock, Howick, Sainte-Barbe, Très-Saint-Sacrement, Ormstown and Saint-Chrysostome.
